modName: Summer bikini UNP UNPB Dream Girl
summary: Bikini for UNP, UNPB BBP, DG (BBP and simple) and heels gloves stockings for DG.
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=5]Description
[/size][/b]
Mod contains bikini for UNP, UNPB BBP, DG BBP and DG simple, (tops and bottoms),
also gloves heels stockings for DG. Heels are craftable in studded.
Number of items in mods for UNP/UNPB and DG is slightly different.
Other items are in chests in Riverwood
Heels requires HDT high heels mod.
BBP files require skeletons that support BBP.

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/69497]Summer bikini for CBBE[/url]
